=Sudimage Redirections=

This is a package for the CMS '''Concrete5'''.
Its purpose is to allow you to redirect a page from the sitemap to another one (without aliasing).

==Usage==

After installing the package, you will have a new page attribute available called ''Redirect this page to another page''.
Then choose a page from the sitemap and the package will redirect the visitor to the target page.

==Localisation==

The package is delivered with a French language .po and .mo file.
More languages are welcome. Fork it and add yours!

